§blogpost
<p>
be it blog posts, emails, or a journal i always keep wanting to write the perfect words and end up not writing. this actually is true for a lot of things in my life, "if you're gonna do it, do it very good". but i'm not very good, and i wont be unless i do things badly first.
</p>

<p>
the fact that this is badly written hurts me inside and makes me want to delete it and stop writing but i'll (hopefully) continue.
</p>

<p>
the takeaway here is:
</p>
<h2>do bad things</h2>
<small>(but not as in evil stuff)</small>
